@startuml seq_13_post_comment
title Sequence Diagram: UC-13 Post Comment

actor User
participant "User Web" as Frontend
participant "Comment Controller" as Controller
participant "Comment Service" as Service
participant "Post Repo" as PostRepo
participant "Comment Repo" as CommentRepo
participant "Event Bus\n(Go Channels)" as EventBus

User -> Frontend: (1.1) Open a post
User -> Frontend: (2.1) Write a comment
User -> Frontend: (3.1) Submit the comment
Frontend -> Controller: (3.2) POST /api/posts/{post_id}/comments {content}
Controller -> Service: (4.1) Create comment request
Service -> PostRepo: (4.2) Validate authentication and post state
PostRepo --> Service: (4.3) Post is valid

Service -> CommentRepo: (5.1) Create comment record
CommentRepo --> Service: (5.2) Comment created
Service -> PostRepo: (6.1) Increment post comment count
PostRepo --> Service: (6.2) Count updated

Service -> EventBus: (6.3) Publish CommentCreatedEvent
note right of EventBus
  Background goroutine notifies
  the post author
end note

Service --> Controller: (7.1) Created comment data
Controller --> Frontend: (7.2) 201 Created
Frontend --> User: (7.3) Render new comment in thread
@enduml
